===============================================================================
ANIMATION IMPLEMENTATION REQUIREMENTS:
===============================================================================

**CSS Transitions (for simple state changes):**
```css
.node {
    transition: all 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0.0, 0.2, 1);
}

.highlight {
    background-color: #FFC107;
    transform: scale(1.1);
}

.fade-in {
    animation: fadeIn 0.5s ease-in;
}

@keyframes fadeIn {
    from { opacity: 0; transform: scale(0.8); }
    to { opacity: 1; transform: scale(1); }
}
```

**JavaScript Animation Queue System (REQUIRED):**
```javascript
class AnimationQueue {
    constructor() {
        this.queue = [];
        this.isPlaying = false;
        this.speed = 1;
    }
    
    add(animationFunction, duration) {
        this.queue.push({ fn: animationFunction, duration: duration });
    }
    
    async play() {
        this.isPlaying = true;
        for (let anim of this.queue) {
            if (!this.isPlaying) break;
            await anim.fn();
            await this.delay(anim.duration / this.speed);
        }
        this.queue = [];
        this.isPlaying = false;
    }
    
    delay(ms) {
        return new Promise(resolve => setTimeout(resolve, ms));
    }
    
    clear() {
        this.queue = [];
        this.isPlaying = false;
    }
}
```

**Specific Animation Patterns:**

1. **Sliding Animation:**
   ```javascript
   element.style.transform = `translateX(${newX}px) translateY(${newY}px)`;
   await delay(400);
   ```

2. **Highlight Pulse:**
   ```javascript
   element.classList.add('highlight');
   await delay(500);
   element.classList.remove('highlight');
   ```

3. **Swap Animation:**
   ```javascript
   // Raise elements
   el1.style.transform = 'translateY(-20px)';
   el2.style.transform = 'translateY(-20px)';
   await delay(200);
   // Cross over
   el1.style.transform = `translateX(${el2X - el1X}px) translateY(-20px)`;
   el2.style.transform = `translateX(${el1X - el2X}px) translateY(-20px)`;
   await delay(400);
   // Lower down
   el1.style.transform = `translateX(${el2X - el1X}px)`;
   el2.style.transform = `translateX(${el1X - el2X}px)`;
   await delay(200);
   ```

4. **Text Update Animation:**
   ```javascript
   explanationText.style.opacity = '0';
   await delay(150);
   explanationText.textContent = newText;
   explanationText.style.opacity = '1';
   ```

